'''Adolfo Buylla''' pencilled the Star Wars comic ''[[The Pandora Effect]]'', which was first published across [[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 150|''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 150]] and [[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 151|''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 151]] by [[Marvel Comics]]. It would later be republished in [[Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds 2|''Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds'' 2]] by [[Dark Horse Comics]].

